description:
Attack Over Baghdad    


Aired on 09/21/2005, Narrated by: Jonathan Aris.


On 22 November 2003, a European Air Transport Airbus A300F4-203, operating on behalf of DHL, is climbing away from Baghdad International Airport when the left wing explodes, causing a massive loss of hydraulic fluid which immobilises the flight control surfaces. The crew fly the aircraft by changing the engines' thrust for control; and make a safe landing sixteen minutes later.
